== 生平與事業 ==
楊升德於2003年在[[紐約州|紐約州]][[紐約|紐約]]出生，父親為身為作家、記者、商人、商業兼媒體顧問楊致和，父母皆為华裔美國人。<ref name="wsj">{{cite web|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/05/02/why-fresh-off-the-boat-tv-series-could-change-the-game/|title=Why the ‘Fresh Off the Boat’ TV Series Could Change the Game - Speakeasy - WSJ|publisher=blogs.wsj.com|accessdate=May 10, 2014|archive-date=2020-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825085604/https://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/05/02/why-fresh-off-the-boat-tv-series-could-change-the-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2002/08/25/style/weddings-vows-heather-ying-and-jeff-yang.html|title=Heather Ying and Jeff Yang|date=25 August 2002|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|accessdate=8 June 2016|archive-date=2018-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180925025836/https://www.nytimes.com/2002/08/25/style/weddings-vows-heather-ying-and-jeff-yang.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2015年起，於{{le|NEST+m|NEST+m}}就學。<ref name="deadline">{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/03/hudson-yang-to-topline-abc-comedy-pilot-far-east-orlando-barry-rothbart-joins-nbcs-love-is-relative/|title=Hudson Yang To Topline ABC Comedy Pilot 'Far East Orlando'; Barry Rothbart Joins NBC's 'Love Is Relative' - Deadline.com|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=May 10, 2014|archive-date=2014-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140520160733/http://www.deadline.com/2014/03/hudson-yang-to-topline-abc-comedy-pilot-far-east-orlando-barry-rothbart-joins-nbcs-love-is-relative/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="imdb">{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/news/ni56919873/|title=Hudson Yang To Topline ABC Comedy Pilot ‘Far East Orlando’; Barry Rothbart Joins NBC’s ‘Love Is Relative’|publisher=[[互聯網電影數據庫|IMDb]]|accessdate=May 10, 2014|archive-date=2018-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181016053452/https://www.imdb.com/news/ni56919873/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年5月11日在Instagram上透露媽媽的工作職位是護士，並祝她母親節快樂

2020年12月18日在Instagram上發佈錄取 Harvard University 哈佛大學的短片，之後在菜鳥新移民某季某集也有真實呈現錄取哈佛大學的劇本橋段

